  title: "\u0110\u1EBFn khu d\xE2n c\u01B0"
  description: "Qua c\xF4ng tr\u01B0\u1EDDng l\xE0 khu d\xE2n c\u01B0 im \u1EAFng.
    Nh\xE0 c\u1EEDa \u0111\xF3ng k\xEDn, kh\xF4ng m\u1ED9t b\xF3ng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi...
    nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng c\xF3 ngh\u0129a l\xE0 an to\xE0n. T\xECm ph\xF2ng an to\xE0n
    \u0111\u1EC3 ngh\u1EC9 ng\u01A1i tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi kh\xE1m ph\xE1 khu v\u1EF1c."
  objective: "\u0110i \u0111\u1EBFn khu d\xE2n c\u01B0 v\xE0 t\xECm ph\xF2ng an to\xE0n"
